OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FIt will be a dry day across the
OL,6,Fregion with early patches of low cloud
OL,7,Fand fog lifting during the morning to
OL,8,Fleave plenty of sunshine. Feeling
OL,9,Fpleasantly warm in the afternoon in
OL,10,Fthe gentle mainly northerly wind.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FIt will remain dry during the
OL,13,Fevening and overnight. There will be
OL,14,Fclear spells, although some low cloud
OL,15,Fis likely to reform, along with a few
OL,16,Fmist or fog patches.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
